    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスライブの前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――営業時間中の喫茶ラビットハウス",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca001.m4a",
      "text": "この街にいる間は、私のことをお姉ちゃんだと思って\n頼ってくれていいからね",
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、お姉ちゃんに任せなさい！　この街のことも\nラビットハウスのこともなんでも聞いてね！",
      "startTime": 13.6999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn001.m4a",
      "text": "またあんなこと言ってます……",
      "startTime": 17.2090069372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ココアさんって、よく「お姉ちゃんって呼んで」って\n言ってるけど、いつもあんな調子なの？",
      "startTime": 23.6464735404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。可愛い子を見るとすぐ\nお姉ちゃんになりたがります。見境がないです",
      "startTime": 30.0999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "でもあの二人、すっかり打ち解けてるね\n千紗さんもココアさんが相手だと話しやすいみたい",
      "startTime": 38.1947046596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？",
      "startTime": 42.1280381439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん、二人は意外と相性がいいのかも",
      "startTime": 43.8338975825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……ココアさんと千紗さんが……",
      "startTime": 48.4338975825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn005.m4a",
      "text": "（どうしてでしょう……）\n（さっきから胸の奥がもやもやします……）",
      "startTime": 57.5333295186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "……チノちゃん？",
      "startTime": 61.8980942961,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5201.901889200002,
          "startTime": 67.0999961853
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の午後",
      "startTime": 65.3980942961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　チノちゃん、どこかにお出かけするの？",
      "startTime": 68.1314154224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、今からすみれさんと出かけてきます",
      "startTime": 71.9787123915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "私が「休憩時間に街を見て回りたい」って話したら\nチノちゃんが道案内してくれることになったんだよ",
      "startTime": 80.0885651903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca004.m4a",
      "text": "それなら私も一緒に行くよ",
      "startTime": 83.5218864676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn007.m4a",
      "text": "道案内なら一人で十分です\nココアさんは他のみなさんと楽しんで下さい",
      "startTime": 89.2333294551,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.666666599988,
          "startTime": 94.9999961217
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn008.m4a",
      "text": "それでは行きましょう、すみれさん",
      "startTime": 92.5012303904,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9198.7657313,
          "startTime": 101.6999961217
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、待ってよチノちゃん！\nそれじゃあ、ココアさん。また後で！",
      "startTime": 98.966662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rabbithouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rabbithouse"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "cca",
      "speakerName": "ココア",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-cca.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-cca005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな～！？",
      "startTime": 102.7379211661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事もあるのに、付き合わせちゃってごめんね",
      "startTime": 107.3143908419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn009.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい\nそれより、街を見て回りたいということですが……",
      "startTime": 113.2999961217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "この街って、木組みの家とか石畳の街並みとか\nとってもおしゃれで素敵だよね",
      "startTime": 122.2127917604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "私もすっかり気に入っちゃって……\n一度ゆっくり街を見てみたかったんだ",
      "startTime": 127.3127917604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn010.m4a",
      "text": "私もこの街が大好きなので\nそんな風に言ってもらえて嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 133.5333294551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn011.m4a",
      "text": "行きたい場所があれば言って下さい\nどこでも案内します",
      "startTime": 138.7333294551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……でも、街のことはよく知らないから……\nじゃあ、チノちゃんの好きな場所に案内してくれる？",
      "startTime": 146.0915294166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_woodentownstreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mokugumi"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chn",
      "speakerName": "チノ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chn_01_01-chn012.m4a",
      "text": "私の好きな場所ですか？\nそれなら……",
      "startTime": 153.0666627884,
      "sfxList": [
